metadata.name: CryptoSlot #1
metadata.description: The NFT CryptoSlot collection is a series of unique digital pictures, each depicting a futuristic cryptocurrency-themed slot machine. Each NFT CryptoSlot has its own unique design and limited edition. NFT CryptoSlot owners have the opportunity to use their pictures to decorate their collections, trade in the NFT market and participate in various competitions and events related to cryptocurrency.
